.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-LOCAL-RATIO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-local-ratio \- FEAT-2739 node-listforwards-local-ratio verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-local-ratio
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compute the ratio of local-origin forwards (payments sent from this node) to the total number of forwards.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBlocal_forward_ratio\fR (0.0\(en1.0), plus \fBlocal_count\fR and \fBtotal_count\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
